## HCU Budget

Keep per-transaction HCU under 20M global, 5M sequential.
High-cost ops: euint64 mul=365K, div=715K, rem=716K.
Silent revert on overflow ‚Äî no error message.

## Common Mistakes (full list: SKILL.md ¬ß L2-06)

| Anti-Pattern | Fix |
|---|---|
| `fhevm-solidity` import | Use `@fhevm/solidity` |
| Missing `ZamaEthereumConfig` | Inherit it |
| No `FHE.allowThis()` after store | Add immediately after assignment |
| `euint256` arithmetic | Use `euint128` or lower |
| Sync decrypt | Use relayer SDK pattern |
| Encrypted divisor in `FHE.div` | Divisor must be plaintext |
| Raw uint input | Wrap in `externalEuintXX` + `FHE.fromExternal()` |
| No reentrancy guard on callback | Add `nonReentrant` |
